Package com.flipfit.exception

package com.flipfit.exception
  • Exceptions
    Class
    Description
    BookingFailedException
    Thrown when a booking operation fails for reasons other than a not-found entity, such as no available seats.
    BookingNotFoundException
    Thrown when a specific booking cannot be found in the database.
    DAOException
    Base exception for all Data Access Object (DAO) related errors.
    DataAccessException
    Thrown to indicate a general data access problem, typically wrapping a SQLException.
    DuplicateUserException
    Thrown when an attempt is made to create a user that already exists (e.g., with a duplicate email or username).
    GymNotFoundException
    Thrown when a specific gym cannot be found in the database.
    PaymentFailedException
    Thrown when a payment processing operation fails.
    SlotNotFoundException
    Thrown when a specific time slot cannot be found in the database.
    UserNotFoundException
    Thrown when a specific user cannot be found in the database.
